prefix=/workspace/catkin_ws/devel

Name: ouster_ros
Description: Description of ouster_ros
Version: 0.5.1
Cflags: -I/workspace/catkin_ws/devel/include -I/workspace/catkin_ws/src/Ouster/src/ouster_example/ouster_ros/include -I/workspace/catkin_ws/src/Ouster/src/ouster_example/ouster_ros/../ouster_client/include -I/workspace/catkin_ws/src/Ouster/src/ouster_example/ouster_ros/../ouster_client/include/optional-lite -I/usr/include/eigen3
Libs: -L${prefix}/lib -louster_ros
Requires: roscpp message_runtime std_msgs sensor_msgs geometry_msgs
